msgstr ""

#: ../../../compiler/architecture-overview.md:283
msgid "MIR optimization"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../compiler/architecture-overview.md:283
msgid ""
"Inlining, constant propagation, dead code elimination -- all applied before "
